Questions.qstn: Of the films Empty Set Studios released last year, 60% were comedies and the rest were horror films. 75% of the comedies were profitable, but 75% of the horror moves were unprofitable. If the studio made a total of 40 films, and broke even on none of them, how many of their films were profitable?

Guests at a recent party ate a total of fifteen hamburgers. Each guest who was neither a student nor a vegetarian ate exactly one hamburger. No hamburger was eaten by any guest who was a student, a vegetarian, or both. If half of the guests were vegetarians, how many guests attended the party?
Questions.qstnStmt1: (1) The vegetarians attended the party at a rate of 2 students to every 3 non-students, half the rate for non-vegetarians.
Questions.qstnStmt2: (2) 30% of the guests were vegetarian non-students
